    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged and bounded: the single F1717 load condition is the regulatory standard condition, and the E/uval metric demonstrates adequate predictive accuracy within that condition. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision for this Class II device submission. Package is issued under ProfileMinimal; a hash is provided for content integrity but no digital signature has been applied to this package.",
